{"tid":1776432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"余英時斥習如「現代秦始皇」","createTime":"2019-12-09T13:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T08:16:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"03958d35a3554229877d7fc7660575bba3640d47","tid":1776432,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:57:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191209/7HWAEXVXONXMLNBXCO332QL6FY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191209%2F7HWAEXVXONXMLNBXCO332QL6FY%2F&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=a59842ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191209%2F7HWAEXVXONXMLNBXCO332QL6FY%2F&h=9f6cdff4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191209/7HWAEXVXONXMLNBXCO332QL6FY/</a><br />\n<br />\n余英時斥習如「現代秦始皇」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191209/large/1575819598_a304.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191209%2Flarge%2F1575819598_a304.gif&h=85b240ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大量經書在文革時期被毀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【新聞背景】<br />\n<br />\n習近平當政七年來，對涉意識形態的新聞出版、文化教育等控制空前嚴格；對學術界和知識分子的控制也遠超前朝鄧小平、江澤民、胡錦濤時代，不少專家學者因言論與當局觀點不同備受打壓，或受公安警告不能發聲、或被開除黨籍公職、甚或被加以刑事罪名送入監獄；內地知識精英噤若寒蟬，紛移民國外。學者直指這是新時代「坑儒」，習是「現代秦始皇」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n非議中共即受打壓<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：清除政敵檔案 防死灰復燃<br />\n<br />\n近兩年被中共整肅的知識精英，包括清華大學法學院教授許章潤，許因網上撰文批評習被校方撤職，大幅削減工資待遇，校方還成立工作組對他調查；廈門大學歷史系助理教授周運中，以及廈大經濟學教授尤盛東，因在課堂上非議中共，遭校方解僱；貴州大學經濟學教授楊紹政，因撰文質疑中共體制浪費公帑被校方開除；中南財經大學副教授翟桔紅，因在課堂上談論中共修憲、國企制度及人民代表大會制度，被開除黨籍、取消教師資格。<br />\n<br />\n此外，還有北京師範大學史傑鵬教授、山東工商學院李默海教授、重慶師範大學譚松副教授等，都因言論遭校方解僱。著名國學家余英時曾指，今時中共的「焚書坑儒」與秦始皇時代不同，「時代變了，今天的書主要在網絡。用不着燒，也不能燒，禁止你出現。三個人在一起說話，只要有妄議中央之類，就可以把你關起來；這就是新的坑儒。」余直指，「沒想到毛澤東死後幾十年，中國又來了一個現代秦始皇習近平！」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"37356ed3dcc2969ebcbdf505bb3cdf7df6160ea1","tid":1776432,"uid":318264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"秦國最後嘅下場係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8389c09faaac6dfdaea37d0ef2c60c126c9ed977","tid":1776432,"uid":283438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"秦朝好似得十五年就亡咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c57544e00cfbdacea9a086cc613042ece4453b4","tid":1776432,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37356ed3dcc2969ebcbdf505bb3cdf7df6160ea1","tid":1776432,"uid":318264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"秦國最後嘅下場係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"下一個獨裁開始"},{"pid":"8094314e589836f6a3cadbf0c8c26329f3963676","tid":1776432,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:18:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbe0768a9682e5767be56f4dbd9b648a9975d944","tid":1776432,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hqsbonline.files.wordpress.com/2016/12/272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhqsbonline.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F12%2F272.jpg&h=cc33c5c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca8e8dbc95b4f4d57aa2cc7b563f7ff56d93c131","tid":1776432,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTFFAqu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTFFAqu.jpg&h=2b4a514e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b1409c359d37888b07f6ebd0f591ee888b613f3","tid":1776432,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"新亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi